{"tid":1980260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港人打乜撚國際戰線?","createTime":"2020-04-20T03:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T03:48:36.000Z","uid":175309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b4d5511b8c4a88da83a9495f0bbb7e843f5fc79","tid":1980260,"uid":175309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:33:23.000Z","msg":"中國越來越明目張膽,打定主意要直接收回香港,一國一制<br />\n靠香港人自己同政府,基本上無用,好聽攬炒,難聽就等死<br />\n唯一出路就係靠外國打救<br />\n國際線應運而生,將香港既情況放上twitter等外國知道,製造輿論,令美國或其他外國出手救香港<br />\n但問題係香港人打乜撚國際戰?圍爐打飛機就叻<br />\n用<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=932acd2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> <br />\n經常有一堆twitter推薦叫你幫手去rt&amp;like<br />\n然後回覆好易搵到一堆用連豬,連狗,防毒面具,五大訴求等等做icon既ac,例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GdWHBzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGdWHBzQ.jpg&h=fda67f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入一入去睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgH35um.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgH35um.jpg&h=67a24206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哇,千幾follower喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azXcerQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazXcerQ.jpg&h=4791cbd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去碌極都係香港人follow<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nub8w9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnub8w9T.jpg&h=a488ec7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xAF1R9U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAF1R9U.jpg&h=f89c0a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回覆都只有香港rt&amp;like,外國人理都唔撚理<br />\n有d個profile入到去,外國人睇到根本只會當係bot<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JEDZDQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJEDZDQK.jpg&h=49699e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有d回覆就乜都無,淨放#tag,入去睇一睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjOfcbi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfjOfcbi.jpg&h=687a1504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbot來架?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otBXqwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotBXqwq.jpg&h=062c5daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n堆follower又係一堆香港人 <br />\n你打國際線,一個外國人都唔follow你,你只係上twitter做本地文宣,有乜撚用?圍爐打飛機,開ig上連登得啦,用乜撚twitter?<br />\n的確,你用#chinavirus, #ccp, #chinazi, #chinaliedpeopledied 呢類#tag, 有<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搜尋開,睇開呢d</span></span></strong> #tag既外國人係會睇到<br />\n而且呢堆#tag因為<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">關中国同疫情事</span></span></span></strong>,所以先多人搜尋<br />\n你用#hongkonger, #standwithhongkong, #glorytohongkong, #hongkongpoliceterrorism <br />\n撚有外國人會搜尋?撚有外國人會知,你係撚打緊國際線?用番連登啦,用番ig啦<br />\n一堆人以為自己rt&amp;like左百幾個post就做左野<br />\n你係刷大左個rt&amp;like既數字<br />\n但根本就無外國人理鳩你<br />\n實際根本就無令外國人知道香港既野<br />\n李柱銘單野都係本身件事夠轟動先多人講<br />\n但都係好快就沉左<br />\n因為呢件事得番香港人互相rt&amp;like,外國人,who cares? 無睇開喎,咁沉左就由佢架啦<br />\n疫情係疫情,中共要屌<br />\n但香港既野?who cares? <br />\n奶茶聯盟?香港單方面幫人retweet緊咋,你有見到泰國人rt番香港警暴同而家廿三條既野再煲大咩?無呀,點解?因為佢地無跟開,香港人又淨係圍爐打飛機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國人分分鐘連廿三條係咩都唔知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人打乜撚國際戰線?<br />\n打番本地文宣圍爐算啦"},{"pid":"058461fec89a66e0e70e1b7d786011f6b7d00bc7","tid":1980260,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"?"}]}